snippet: Yelp filed an objection to a proposed antitrust settlement, complaining that search results favor Google Plus Local.
abstract: Online review service Yelp joins critics formally opposing European Union's proposed antitrust settlement with Google; Yelp says in its filing in antitrust case that results on Google's search engine favor Google Plus Local, a direct Yelp competitor.
lead_paragraph: Yelp filed an objection to a proposed antitrust settlement, complaining that search results favor Google Plus Local.

headline.main: Yelp Joins Critics of European Union Antitrust Settlement With Google
headline.print_headline: Yelp Joins Critics of European Union Antitrust Settlement With Google
